"16:36:20" : {s: 16, a: 36, w: 20, r: "ضلل", t: "ٱلضَّلَٰلَةُ", l: "ضَلَٰلَة", lc: 9, tl: "l-ḍalālatu", lb: "পথভ্রষ্টতা",e: "the straying", b: "গোমরাহী", i: "kesesatan", f: 2, rm: "Erred, strayed, or went astray. Deviated from the right way or course. Missed or lost the right way. Lost something but does not know its place. Confounded or perplexed and unable to see the right course.", ag: "ال التعريف وأسم مرفوع", eg: "Determiner al and Noun Nominative case", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "NOM", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "F", num: "", mood: "", lu: "أَضَلَّ،أَضَلُّ،ضَلَّ"},
